<body>
<h1>Imagined Communities Bab 2 - Dengan Kutipan dari Buku Benedict Anderson</h1>
<div class="container">

<button class="accordion-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="content1" id="btn1">⚰️ Kematian, Agama dan Nasionalisme</button>
<div class="content-panel" id="content1" role="region" aria-labelledby="btn1">
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent1a" id="subbtn1a">1. Pengertian Kematian Tradisional</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent1a" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn1a">
    <p>Dalam buku ini, Anderson menekankan pentingnya ritual kematian dan kepercayaan agama dalam membentuk solidaritas dan identitas komunitas sebelum masa nasionalisme.</p>
    <blockquote>"Religious celebrations of death often reinforce the solidarity of community across generations, serving as a binding force."</blockquote>
    <p>Kematian dalam konteks ini bukan sekadar akhir individu tetapi juga momen solidaritas kolektif yang diproses secara spiritual.</p>
  </div>
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent1b" id="subbtn1b">2. Peran Ritual Agama</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent1b" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn1b">
    <p>Ritual agama berfungsi tidak hanya sebagai kegiatan sakral tetapi sebagai mekanisme sosial yang menciptakan rasa kebersamaan dan keterikatan emosional.</p>
    <blockquote>"The emotional power of religious ritual lies in its ability to connect individuals to a larger, imagined community."</blockquote>
  </div>
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent1c" id="subbtn1c">3. Perubahan Konsep Kematian dalam Nasionalisme</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent1c" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn1c">
    <p>Nasionalisme mengalihkan makna kematian ke ranah duniawi sebagai pengorbanan untuk negara dan komunitas yang diimajinasikan.</p>
    <blockquote>"Death acquires a new political meaning insofar as individuals conceive themselves as members of an imagined community for whom sacrifice is demanded."</blockquote>
  </div>
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent1d" id="subbtn1d">4. Simbolisme Kematian dan Solidaritas Kebangsaan</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent1d" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn1d">
    <p>Simbol kematian dalam perang dan peringatan nasional memperkokoh rasa solidaritas dan kesetiaan atas dasar imajinasi kebangsaan.</p>
    <blockquote>"National mourning rituals transform death into a powerful symbol of collective identity and political unity."</blockquote>
  </div>
  </div>

<button class="accordion-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="content2" id="btn2">🏛️ Sistem Budaya Pra Nasionalisme</button>
<div class="content-panel" id="content2" role="region" aria-labelledby="btn2">
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent2a" id="subbtn2a">1. Struktur Sosial dan Identitas Lokal</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent2a" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn2a">
    <p>Identitas dalam sistem pra nasionalisme terbentuk atas jaringan sosial yang nyata seperti kerabat, agama, dan wilayah kecil.</p>
    <blockquote>"Before nationalism, people’s identities were grounded in tangible, localized communities marked by kinship and religion."</blockquote>
  </div>
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent2b" id="subbtn2b">2. Agama dan Kepercayaan dalam Komunitas</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent2b" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn2b">
    <p>Agama dan kepercayaan bersama berperan sebagai pusat identitas dan solidaritas sosial masyarakat tradisional.</p>
    <blockquote>"Religious beliefs and shared sacred rituals provided the emotional glue binding pre-modern communities."</blockquote>
  </div>
  </div>

<button class="accordion-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="content3" id="btn3">⏳ Persepsi Waktu: Perubahan Fundamental</button>
<div class="content-panel" id="content3" role="region" aria-labelledby="btn3">
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent3a" id="subbtn3a">1. Persepsi Siklus Waktu Tradisional</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent3a" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn3a">
    <p>Konsep waktu tradisional yang bersifat siklis dan berulang mencerminkan struktur sosial dan agama masyarakat pra-nasionalistis.</p>
    <blockquote>"Time was experienced as cyclical and repetitive, tied to ritual and natural cycles."</blockquote>
  </div>
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent3b" id="subbtn3b">2. Dampak Teknologi Cetak Terhadap Persepsi Waktu</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent3b" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn3b">
    <p>Penemuan teknologi cetak memungkinkan persepsi waktu linier dan simultan, menyebarkan kesadaran komunitas kebangsaan yang baru.</p>
    <blockquote>"The printing press produced simultaneously consumable texts that restructured people’s experience of time and history."</blockquote>
  </div>
  </div>

<button class="accordion-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="content4" id="btn4">📰 Bentuk Imajinasi Baru: Novel dan Surat Kabar</button>
<div class="content-panel" id="content4" role="region" aria-labelledby="btn4">
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent4a" id="subbtn4a">1. Peran Novel dalam Bahasa Standar</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent4a" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn4a">
    <p>Novel berfungsi sebagai alat pembentukan bahasa nasional dan imajinasi bersama dalam komunitas kebangsaan.</p>
    <blockquote>"Novels helped to spread a standardized language and create a shared cultural lexicon."</blockquote>
    </div>
  <button class="subtopic-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="subcontent4b" id="subbtn4b">2. Surat Kabar sebagai Media Nasionalisme</button>
  <div class="nested-content" id="subcontent4b" role="region" aria-labelledby="subbtn4b">
    <p>Surat kabar memainkan peranan penting dalam mengkonstruksi ruang publik dan pengalaman nasional secara serempak.</p>
    <blockquote>"Newspapers forged a temporal simultaneity that allowed readers to imagine themselves as part of the nation."</blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
<script>
  const accordionButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-button');
  accordionButtons.forEach(button => {
    button.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const expanded = button.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
      button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(!expanded));
      button.classList.toggle('active');
      const panel = document.getElementById(button.getAttribute('aria-controls'));
      if (!expanded) {
        panel.classList.add('open');
      } else {
        panel.classList.remove('open');
      }
    });
  });

  const subtopicButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.subtopic-button');
  subtopicButtons.forEach(button => {
    button.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const expanded = button.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
      button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(!expanded));
      button.classList.toggle('active');
      const panel = document.getElementById(button.getAttribute('aria-controls'));
      if (!expanded) {
        panel.classList.add('open');
      } else {
        panel.classList.remove('open');
      }
    });
  });
</script>
